 data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/00637L\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00637L-TW</a>)</p></section><section><p>4. 外資累計買超 2 日的股票<br/>旺宏 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2337:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2337\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2337-TW</a>)、群益優選非投等債 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:00953B:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/00953B\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00953B-TW</a>)、南亞科 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2408:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2408\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2408-TW</a>)、華邦電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2344:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2344\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2344-TW</a>)、元晶 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6443:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6443\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6443-TW</a>)</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>5. 外資當日 (05) 買超的股票<br/>聯電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2303:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2303\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2303-TW</a>)、群益優選非投等債 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:00953B:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/00953B\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" targ